query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 b q1 s t1 tq1 u1 acc) */ select count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 0 AND q1.favorite_count <= 1
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('ag.algebraic-geometry',
'bash',
'co.combinatorics',
'dg.differential-geometry',
'electromagnetism',
'gr.group-theory',
'homework-and-exercises',
'javascript',
'pr.probability',
'quantum-field-theory',
'shell')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 0 AND u1.downvotes <= 1
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('es',
'mathoverflow',
'physics',
'unix')
inner join badge AS b
on b.user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Announcer',
'Caucus',
'Constituent',
'Disciplined',
'Explainer',
'Favorite Question',
'Quorum',
'Suffrage')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id;
